{
  "stem": "25831.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I remember the day exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was January 30th, 1933.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my mother and I came back from a visit in the early afternoon and passed a kiosk.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the headline on the papers were 'Hitler Appointed Chancellor.' And we felt troubled.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we continued talking about the things we had talked about before.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And when we sat down for dinner-- my father had come home-- we again mentioned the fact that Hitler had been appointed chancellor.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my sister said, well, it can't be so terrible because Thuringen-- that's Thuringia, which is a province of Prussia-- no, of Saxony-- has a Nazi prime minister and nothing has happened there which is particularly upsetting.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we all went on with our normal conversations and our normal tasks.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "My father took his brief nap and went back to the office.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "My sister and I did our homework.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "She diligently, I reluctantly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And in the afternoon we did what we always did, I'm sure.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "We went to the bakery and got a freshly-baked roll for the afternoon-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] vesper, it was called.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Vesper is the Latin word for afternoon, also the Italian word for afternoon.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The afternoon meal was called vesper-- V-E-S-P-E-R.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "There's an opera too, by Verdi.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then life went on quite normally for a few hours until either that-- oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "That evening I was glued to the radio.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Each one of us had a radio in our room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I listened to the military music which was played during the torchlight parade for Hitler in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "It was on the [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Potsdam ?] Street, [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Potsdam ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Strasse. ?] And I loved military music.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And then I listened to Hitler's speech, which I often imitated.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
